value.title: Fact check: Video shows police collecting discarded Amazon packages, not thousands of Trump ballots
value.excerpt: Social media users have claimed a video shows police finding thousands of ballots for U.S. President Donald Trump dumped in a field. This is not true; local police report that the footage actually shows discarded Amazon packages.
